---
title: Fried Chicken and Honey Butter Bacon Burger with Sesame Wedges, Spicy Mayo and Bang Bang Cucumber
description: This Fried Chicken and Honey Butter Bacon Burger is a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fried-chicken-and-honey-butter-bacon-burger-94865447-f41c15ea.jpg
